{"tid":1170333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣駐美「北美事務協調委員會」更名「台灣美國事務委員會」（Taiwan Council for US Affairs）","createTime":"2019-05-25T02:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T04:32:53.000Z","uid":35790,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1dc5db41dbf8daafa942744ba881ddd0b7dd4078","tid":1170333,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"台灣入名 「北美事務協調委員會」更名「台灣美國事務委員會」<br />\n<br />\n2019-05-25<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕隨著台美關係提升，我國外交部推特上指出，「北美事務協調委員會」將更名為「台灣美國事務委員會」，已明確反映其工作內涵。<br />\n<br />\n外交部表示，「北美事務協調委員會」是在1979年，相應於美國成立「美國在台協會」（American Institute in Taiwan，AIT）而設立，作為AIT的對等機構。經由跟美方充分協調溝通後，如今決定將「北美事務協調委員會」（Coordination Council for North American Affairs，CCNAA）更名為「台灣美國事務委員會」（Taiwan Council for US Affairs，TCUSA）。<br />\n<br />\n另據了解，至於全稱為「台北駐美國經濟文化代表處（TECRO）」的駐美代表處，目前並無跟進正名「台灣」的規劃。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"0c7a5da7112eb6910683031c0db7aaedb0ab2986","tid":1170333,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"等睇中國外交部發言"},{"pid":"c6d4be802800f86f45a940af24811188f16236b0","tid":1170333,"uid":51840,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T02:51:13.000Z","msg":"下一步就係升格為大使館"},{"pid":"cf5b9775331bbbf4a042dcd76dd287b614b0bca1","tid":1170333,"uid":197196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"直接同台灣建交啦"},{"pid":"47753761f54f26c9c8a8846a5480d61156725c88","tid":1170333,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:17:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a790e7f0c3dee80b5cb0011a47632b7f800cb1e9","tid":1170333,"uid":35790,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:20:16.000Z","msg":"「台灣美國事務委員會」（Taiwan Council for US Affairs，TCUSA）<br />\n<br />\n中國話要乎合一中原則<br />\n台灣之前要加上中國(中國台灣)<br />\n<br />\n「中國台灣美國事務委員會」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"388f81ee0695d80fae60e2ed3764d2af7e3a1002","tid":1170333,"uid":216664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:21:02.000Z","msg":"【6.9反惡法】 <br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道"},{"pid":"d1e99e0010cb69711a9e27d8ee7978fe860e8866","tid":1170333,"uid":251074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T03:49:52.000Z","msg":"快d亮劍啦 ，比美帝自清楚自主研發的飛機飛彈航母。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5cd68530786224ed89e37f6d8d061aeadcf630","tid":1170333,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T04:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}